It's a broad question. Measure, yeah, so we, you know, many of you may have seen like, you know,

00:48:06.239 --> 00:48:11.520
data science is three different, you know, this Venn diagram, there's the coding part of it,

00:48:11.520 --> 00:48:16.320
there is the math part of it and then there is the business domain part of it, right? So,

00:48:18.879 --> 00:48:23.840
make sure that you are, you know, you're not, you know, you're not, you're not, you know,

00:48:24.159 --> 00:48:34.399
make sure that all three are covered in a project, right? So, and if that's the capability

00:48:34.399 --> 00:48:42.159
side of it. The other big trap is when, say, executives come and say, hey, can you do something

00:48:42.159 --> 00:48:48.320
cool with artificial intelligence or machine learning? So, that is a solution looking for

00:48:48.320 --> 00:48:57.919
a problem and that's a trap, right? Because that has the potential for like, it has the potential

